abilities.name: Wimp Out
abilities.text: During your first turn, this Pokémon has no Retreat Cost

abilities.name: Melodious Healing
abilities.text: Once during your turn, you may heal 30 damage from each of your Water Pokémon

abilities.name: Innards Out
abilities.text: If this Pokémon is in the Active Spot and is Knocked Out by damage from an attack from your opponent's Pokémon, do 50 damage to the Attacking Pokémon

abilities.name: Safeguard
abilities.text: Prevent all damage done to this Pokémonby attacks from your opponent's Pokémon ex

abilities.name: Flower Shield
abilities.text: Each of your Pokémon that has any Psychic Energy attached recovers from all Special Conditions and can't be affected by Special Conditions

abilities.name: Psychic Connect
abilities.text: Once during your turn, you may move all Psychic Energy from 1 of your Benched Psychic Pokémon to your Active Pokémon

abilities.name: Guts
abilities.text: If this Pokémon would be Knocked Out by damage from an attack, flip a coin. If heads, this Pokémon is not Knocked Out and its remaining HP becomes 10

abilities.name: Offload Pass
abilities.text: If this Pokémon is in the Active Spot and is Knocked Out by damage from an attack from your opponent's Pokémon, move all Fighting Energy from this Pokémon to 1 of your Benched Pokémon

abilities.name: Fur Coat
abilities.text: This Pokémon takes -20 damage from attacks

abilities.name: Rising Road
abilities.text: Once during your turn, if this Pokémon is on your Bench, you may switch it with your Active Pokémon

abilities.name: Comatose
abilities.text: As long as this Pokémon is in the Active Spot, whenever you attach an Energy from your Energy Zone to it, it is now Asleep

cards.name: Big Malasada
cards.description: Heal 10 damage and remove a random Special Condition from your Active Pokémon

cards.name: Fishing Net
cards.description: Put a random Basic Water Pokémon from your discard pile into your hand

cards.name: Rare Candy
cards.description: Choose 1 of your Basic Pokémon in play. If you have a stage 2 card in your hand that evolves from that Pokémon, put that card onto the Basic Pokémon to evolve it, skipping the Stage 1. You can't use this card during your first turn or on a Basic Pokémon that was put into play this turn.

cards.name: Rotom Dex
cards.description: Look at the top card of your deck. Then, you may shuffle your deck

cards.name: Poison Barb
cards.description: If the Pokémon this card is attached to is your Active Pokémon and is amaged by an attack from your opponent's Pokémon, the Attacking Pokémon is now Poisoned. Attach Poison Barb to 1 of your Pokémon that doesn't have a Pokémon Tool attached to it.

cards.name: Leaf Cape
cards.description: The Grass Pokémon this card is attached to gets +30 HP. Attach Leaf Cape to 1 of your Pokémon that doesn't have a Pokémon Tool attached to it.

cards.name: Acerola
cards.description: Choose 1 of your Palossand or Mimikyu that has damage on it, and move 40 of its damage to your opponent's Active Pokémon. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Ilima
cards.description: Put 1 of your Colorless Pokémon that has damage on it into your hand. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Kiawe
cards.description: Choose 1 of your Alolan Marowak or Turtonator. Take 2 Fire energy from your Energy Zone and attach it to that Pokémon. Your turn ends.. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Guzma
cards.description: Discard all Pokémon Tool cards attached to each of your opponent's Pokémon. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Lana
cards.description: You can use this card only if you have Araquanid in play. Switch in 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon to the Active Spot.. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Sophocles
cards.description: During this turn, attacks used by your Alolan Golem, Vikavolt or Togedemaru do +30 damage to your opponent's Active Pokémon. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Mallow
cards.description: Heal all damage from 1 of your Shiinotic or Tsareena. If you do, discard all Energy from that Pokémon. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.

cards.name: Lillie
cards.description: Heal 60 damage from 1 of your Stage 2 Pokémon. You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn.
